Package: chlaa
Type: Package
Title: Cholera Outbreak Simulation and Anticipatory Action Modelling
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("OJ", "Watson", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "o.watson15@imperial.ac.uk")
    )
Author: OJ Watson [aut, cre]
Maintainer: OJ Watson <o.watson15@imperial.ac.uk>
URL: https://github.com/OJWatson/chlaa, https://ojwatson.github.io/chlaa/
BugReports: https://github.com/OJWatson/chlaa/issues
Description: Stochastic cholera outbreak model implemented in odin2 with a dust2 backend.
    Provides tools for fitting to outbreak data, simulating counterfactual intervention
    scenarios (vaccination, case management, and WASH), and evaluating outcomes including
    cost-effectiveness and budget allocation.
